HEADWORD: Stupose
<hw>Stu*pose</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>stupa</ets>,
or better <ets>stuppa</ets>, tow. Cf. <er>Stupeous</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Composed of, or having, tufted or matted
filaments like tow; stupeous.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

